right-pagetranslation: Maurk versions o pages fer owersetin
tpt-badtitle: Page name gien ($1) is na ae valit title
tpt-oldrevision:
$2 isna the laitest version o the page [[:$1]].
Yinlie laitest versions can be maurkt fer owersetin.
tpt-notsuitable:
Page $1 isna suitable fer owersetin.
Mak sair that it haes <nowiki><translate></nowiki> tags n haes ae valit syntax.
tpt-saveok: The page [[:$1]] haes been maurkt fer owersetin wi $2 {{PLURAL:$2|owersetin unit|owersetin units}}. The page can nou be [$3 owerset].
tpt-offer-notify: Ye can [$1 tell owerseters] aneat this page.
tpt-badsect: "$1" isna ae valit name fer owerset unit $2.
tpt-showpage-intro:
Ablo new, exeestin n delytit owerset units ar leetit.
Afore maurkin this version fer owersetin, check that the chynges til owerset units ar wee tae avoid onnecessair wairk fer the owerseters.
tpt-duplicate: Owerset unit name $1 is uised mair than yince.
tpt-already-marked: The laitest version o this page haes awreadie been maurkt fer owersetin.
tpt-unmarked: Page $1 is naw langer maurkt fer owersetin.
tpt-list-nopages: Naw pages ar maurkt fer owersetin or readie tae be maurkt fer owersetin.
tpt-new-pages:
{{PLURAL:$1|This page contains|Thir pages contain}} tex wi owersetin tags,
bit naw version o {{PLURAL:$1|this page is|thir pages ar}} nou maurkt fer owersetin.
tpt-old-pages: Some version o {{PLURAL:$1|this page haes|thir pages hae}} been maurkt fer owersetin.
tpt-other-pages:
{{PLURAL:$1|Aen auld version o this page is|Aulder versions o thir pages ar}} maurked fer owersetin,
bit the laitest {{PLURAL:$1|version|versions}} canna be maurkt fer owersetin.
tpt-discouraged-pages: {{PLURAL:$1|This page haes|Thir pages hae}} been discooraged fae further owersetin.
tpt-select-prioritylangs: Comma-separatit leet o prioritie leid codes:

tpt-rev-mark-tooltip: Maurk the laitest version o this page fer owersetin.
tpt-rev-discourage-tooltip: Discoorage further owersetins oan this page.
tpt-rev-encourage-tooltip: Restore this page til normal owersetin.
translate-tag-markthisagain: This page haes [$1 chynges] sin it wis laist [$2 maurkt fer owersetin].
translate-tag-hasnew: This page contains [$1 chynges] that arna maurkt fer owersetin.
tpt-translation-intro: This page is aen [$1 owerset version] o the page [[$2]] n the owersetin is $3% compleate.
tpt-target-page:
This page canna be updated manuallie.
This page is aen owerset o the page [[$1]] n the owersetin can be updated uisin [$2 the owersetin tuil].
tpt-unknown-page:
This namespace is reserved fer content page owersets.
The page that ye'r ettlin tae eedit disna seem tae correspond wi onie page maurkt fer owersetin.
tpt-translation-restricted:
Owersetin o this page intil this leid haes been stapt bi aen owerset admeenistrater.

Reason: $1
tpt-discouraged-language-force: This page canna be owerset intil $2. Aen owerset admeenistrater decided that this page can yinlie be owerset intil $3.
tpt-discouraged-language: Owersetin intil $2 isna ae prioritie fer this page. Aen owerset admeenistrater decided tae focus the owersetin efforts oan $3.
tpt-priority-languages: Aen owerset admeenistrater haes set the prioritie leids fer this groop til $1.
tpt-render-summary: Updatin tae match new version o soorce page
tpt-aggregategroup-remove-confirm: Ar ye sair that ye want tae delyte this aggregate groop?

$1

Multiple Owersetin unit maurkers fer the yin owersetin unit. Owersetin unit tex: 
$1
pt-shake-position:

$1

pt-movepage-action-check: Check gif the muiv is possible
pt-movepage-intro:
This byordinair page permits ye tae muiv pages that ar maurkt fer owersetin.
The muiv action will na be instant, cause monie pages will need tae be muived.
While the pages ar bein muived, it's na possible tae interact wi the said pages.
Failures will be loggit in the [[Special:Log/pagetranslation|page owersetin log]] n thay need tae be repaired bi haun.
pt-movepage-started:
The base page haes nou been muived.
Please check the [[Special:Log/pagetranslation|page owersetin log]] fer mistaks n compleation message.
pt-locked-page: This page is lockt cause the owersetable page is nou bein muived.
pt-deletepage-invalid-text: The speceefied page isna aen owersetable page or aen owersetin page.
pt-deletepage-action-check: Leet the pages tae be delytit
pt-deletepage-any-legend: Delyte owersetable page or owersetin page
pt-deletepage-started: Please check the [[Special:Log/pagetranslation|page owersetin log]] fer mistaks n compleation message.
pt-deletepage-intro:
This byordinair page permits ye tae delyte ae hale owersetable page, or aen indiveedual owersetin page in ae leid.
The delyte action willna be instant, cause aw the pages dependin oan thaim will be delytit ava.
Failures will be loggit in the [[Special:Log/pagetranslation|page owersetin log]] n thay need tae be repaired bi haun.
